*
* -   \\(\operatorname{log1p}(x) = \mathrm{NaN}\\) with signal if \\(x < -1\\) (including \\(-\infty\\))
* -   \\(\operatorname{log1p}(+\infty) = +\infty\\)
* -   \\(\operatorname{log1p}(-1) = -\infty\\) with signal
* -   \\(\operatorname{log1p}(\mathrm{NaN})= \mathrm{NaN}\\) with no signal
*
